HTC Advances in Taipei After Third-Quarter Sales Forecast Tops Estimates

-- B y   T i m   C u l p a n
-- 
2011-08-01T01:04:12Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-08-01/htc-advances-in-taipei-after-third-quarter-sales-forecast-tops-estimates.html
HTC Corp. (2498)  shares climbed in Taipei
trading after the company forecast revenue this quarter which
surpassed analyst estimates.  HTC added 2.8 percent to NT$882 as of 9:01 a.m., compared
with a 0.1 percent advance in the benchmark Taiex index.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Tim Culpan in Taipei at 
